title: Joe Hartzler
description: Happy New Year, weirdos! We are back with the hilarious and thoughtful Joe Hartzler (comedy! improv! THANKSKILLING 3!), fresh off a week of shooting a series of commercials with Pete, Pete wanted to record an ep with one of the funniest guys he's worked with ever and this is the result. GET INTO IT and a crispy 2013 to you all!
